snippet: Foul trouble kept Nikola Jokic from playing more minutes the past two games. He showed what he can do when he stays on the floor....
lead_paragraph: Foul trouble kept Nikola Jokic from playing more minutes the past two games. He showed what he can do when he stays on the floor.
